title: Guest mix - SETI Project - Inner Worlds Album Promomix  #psychedelictrance #goatrance #psytrance
description:
A promotional mix of my Album "Inner Words" Out on Timewarp Records 11-04-2025.  @Geomagnetic‬ ‪@GeomagneticRecords‬ 
https://www.beatport.com/release/inner-worlds/5030009

#psychedelictrance #goatrance #live #psytrancemix  #goaparty #psytrancefamily #psytrancepeople #psytrancefestivals #psytrancecommunity 

SETI Project by Guido Venier  is a legendary Acid-Goa-Trance project from the 90s.
The journey of SETI Project into Trance music began in the late 1990ies and is about to continue into the future. Heavily inspired by Astral Projection, Tsujoshi Suzuki and Logic Bomb, to name a few, Guido creates a unique blend of Psy- and Goatrance with a touch of Acid Techno heavily rooted in classic Goa music but also looking ahead. The name of the project is derived from the equivocal scientific project dedicated to the search of intelligent alien life.

For booking mail to: guido@seti-project.com

Social links
https://linktr.ee/setiproject

title: Guest mix - SETI Project - Space Walk Album Promo(Acid-Goa-Trance) #psychedelictrance  #goatrance
description:
A promotional mix of my Album "Space Walk" Out on @SuntripRecords‬
get your copy at https://www.beatport.com/release/space-walk/4572565

SETI Project by Guido Venier  is a legendary Acid-Goa-Trance project from the 90s.
The journey of SETI Project into Trance music began in the late 1990ies and is about to continue into the future. Heavily inspired by Astral Projection, Tsujoshi Suzuki and Logic Bomb, to name a few, Guido creates a unique blend of Psy- and Goatrance with a touch of Acid Techno heavily rooted in classic Goa music but also looking ahead. The name of the project is derived from the equivocal scientific project dedicated to the search of intelligent alien life.

For booking mail to: guido@seti-project.com

title: Psychedelic Trance guest mix by  Dennyck a  twilight fullon mix
description:
Bio:
Dennyck is the first musical project by the Italian DJ & Music producer Davide Nicolucci, 
who is currently based in Bangkok, Thailand. 
With over 20 years experience and music creation & selection among different underground styles was Rave music, Psytrance, Psydub, Goa Trance and progressive.
Dennyck provides a psychedelic trip to his listeners with each mix, as well as at live shows and   DJ sets at various events and festivals. 
He has performed in Psytrance events in Italy, Japan, Thailand, Vietnam, Philippines, Sweden and more. 
Dennyck is also the mind and soul behind the outdoor parties "Dreamland Psytrance" happening in Koh Phangan and around Thailand.

Influenced at a fairly young age during the rise of outdoor parties situated along the Mid North Coast of Australia, he quickly grasped the fundamentals of music production and began crafting. This sonic sound may just be the beginning, as it is consistently developing, evolving and finding a signature middle groove. Bringing new ideas to fruition from every crevice of his mind.

title: Psychedelic Trance Guest mix - Alienatic   Live Set At Universo Paralello Brazil 2023
description:
Alienatic is a fast-rising psychedelic trance project from Holland, led by Jake van Aarst, also known as Jakaan. Jake has been involved in the psytrance scene for many years, both as a DJ and as a producer of his progressive psytrance project, Jakaan.
Alienatic's style is characterized by its uptempo, full-on beats, funky baselines, dreamy atmospheres, and unique, otherworldly sounds that give it a distinct, alien-like quality. The project quickly gained popularity, with its tracks and remixes being well-received by fans of the genre.
In 2020, Alienatic signed with the prestigious UK-based label Nano Records, which has helped to further propel the project's success. With collaborations with some of the biggest names in the industry, such as Killerwatts, Ital, and Ajja, Alienatic is poised for continued success in the world of psychedelic trance.
So, for those who love the full-on, uptempo style of psychedelic trance, Alienatic is definitely a project to keep an eye on! Stay Alien !
